serve-this
==========

Serve the contents of the current directory,
like it was running on a server.

Example
=======

  $ serve-this
  *****
  serving ~/some/directory on port 9292

Push it to Heroku!
==================

  config.ru

    require 'serve-this'
    run ServeThis.from(Dir.pwd)

Note
====

this doesnt work yet!
